// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1935 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 634cbc9a-306b-5390-9ed0-a718281546d5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*almalinux:10*" or process.executable like~ "*almalinux:9*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:9*")
